translation[6]{c,v,t}:
  9,21,"INkosi yabo Ibanika iindaba ezivuyisayo zeNceba evela kuYo, yaye Ikholisekile (ngabo), nayiMiyezo yabo ekukho ulonwabo lwanaphakade"
  9,22,Baya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade. Inene kuAllâh kukho umvuzo omkhulu
  9,23,Hini na nina bakholwayo! Musani ukuthabatha ootata benu nabantakwenu nibenze abakhuseli benu ukuba basakhetha ukungakholwa kunokukholwa. Nabani na kuni owenza loo nto ungomnye wabagabadeli
  9,24,"Yithi: “Ukuba ngaba ooyihlo benu, oonyana benu, abantakwenu, abafazi benu, izizalwana zenu, ubutyebi benu enibuzuzileyo, ushishino lwenu enoyikisela ukuncipha kwalo nemizi yenu eninamabhongo ngayo zezona zinto zithandeka kakhulu kuni kunoAllâh noMthunywa waKhe nokuzabalaza ngamandla nokulwa eNdleleni yaKhe, lindani ke de uAllâh Azise isigqibo saKhe kodwa uAllâh Akabakhokeli abantu abangabenzi bobubi"
  9,25,"Inene uAllâh Uninike uloyiso kumadabi amaninzi kananjalo ngeMini yedabi laseHunayn, nisavuyiswa bubuninzi benu, suke (obo buninzi benu) banganincedi nto, nomhlaba, ngoku umkhulu kangaka, wacutheka kuni, naza nabaleka nina"
  9,26,"Ke Yena uAllâh Wathulula ukuthozama phezu koMthunywa (uMuhammad) nakumakholwa, Wathumela imikhosi (yeengelosi) enaningayiboni nina, wabohlwaya abangakholwayo. Lowo ngumvuzo wabangakholwayo"